340
00:17:32,180 --> 00:17:35,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't have many expressions. 
This is the best I can do.</i></font>

341
00:17:35,620 --> 00:17:38,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're not fooling anybody! 
You're taking the piss for sure!</i></font>

342
00:17:38,900 --> 00:17:40,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Crap!</i></font>

343
00:17:40,090 --> 00:17:43,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kirino gains nothing from 
hanging around this vulgar bunch!</i></font>

344
00:17:43,550 --> 00:17:45,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's true!</font>

345
00:17:45,890 --> 00:17:49,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kirino, just focus on winning!</i></font>

346
00:17:49,730 --> 00:17:51,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know you can do this!</i></font>

347
00:17:51,490 --> 00:17:54,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's to show them the fruits 
of all your practice!</i></font>

348
00:17:56,760 --> 00:17:59,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ded...</font>

349
00:17:59,020 --> 00:18:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Bwahaha, I win!</i></font>

350
00:17:59,220 --> 00:18:03,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}SUMERAGI IKON - 4TH PLACE OUT OF 4</font>

351
00:18:01,030 --> 00:18:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You just got lucky with the items!</i></font>

352
00:18:06,320 --> 00:18:08,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Bucky. I lost.</font>

353
00:18:08,910 --> 00:18:12,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is what it is. Contests can 
be decided by luck at times.</font>

354
00:18:12,030 --> 00:18:14,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We'll have to bid farewell 
to all the people who lost.</i></font>

355
00:18:14,870 --> 00:18:18,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The winners, please move 
to this waiting room.</i></font>

356
00:18:18,250 --> 00:18:22,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yours truly lost? Not to mention 
we were dead last.</i></font>

357
00:18:23,030 --> 00:18:25,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I should've researched the game more.</i></font>

358
00:18:25,410 --> 00:18:30,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, before that, I should've 
foreseen this kind of treatment!</i></font>

359
00:18:30,090 --> 00:18:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What an utter disgrace I am!</i></font>

360
00:18:32,380 --> 00:18:35,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A Yamabuki is supposed to be 
no less than perfect!</i></font>

361
00:18:38,450 --> 00:18:42,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Kirino. This is all my fault.</font>

362
00:18:42,780 --> 00:18:43,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They...</font>

363
00:18:43,940 --> 00:18:45,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were so awesome!</font>

364
00:18:45,850 --> 00:18:48,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe how good they were!</font>

365
00:18:48,210 --> 00:18:53,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, I wasn't able to talk to Ao-chan, 
but I'm glad I got to be a part of this.</font>

366
00:18:53,230 --> 00:18:57,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, Kirino, don't you hate 
how you were treated?</font>

367
00:18:57,290 --> 00:19:00,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, it was frustrating 
that I couldn't get back at them...</font>

368
00:19:01,860 --> 00:19:03,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But more than that,</font>

369
00:19:03,040 --> 00:19:07,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy that our hard work 
got us such a big stage.</font>

370
00:19:09,030 --> 00:19:13,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It made me believe that together, we can 
make even more amazing things happen!</font>

371
00:19:15,230 --> 00:19:18,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never thought of it that way before.</font>

372
00:19:18,540 --> 00:19:21,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems I was too fixated on results.</font>

373
00:19:21,560 --> 00:19:24,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's most important is 
that you had fun.</font>

374
00:19:24,730 --> 00:19:26,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? Did you have fun?</font>

375
00:19:26,770 --> 00:19:27,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep!</font>

376
00:19:27,630 --> 00:19:30,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good to hear. However...</font>

377
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:33,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't let those jerks get away 
with the crap they gave you!</font>

378
00:19:33,820 --> 00:19:37,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How dare they hurt my Kirino 
right in front of me?!</font>

379
00:19:37,360 --> 00:19:40,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Momotose Ao invited you and 
didn't even interact with you! How rude!</font>

380
00:19:40,930 --> 00:19:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen up, Kirino!</font>

381
00:19:42,490 --> 00:19:44,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're trying again!</font>

382
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:46,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time, we'll make direct 
contact with Momotose Ao!</font>

383
00:19:46,930 --> 00:19:48,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Uh...</font>

384
00:19:48,800 --> 00:19:52,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, Bucky, did you just...</font>

385
00:19:53,930 --> 00:19:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

386
00:19:57,340 --> 00:19:59,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ao-chan's calling!</font>

387
00:19:57,340 --> 00:19:59,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}MOMOTOSE AO</font>

388
00:19:59,260 --> 00:20:01,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! Let me have a word with her!</font>

389
00:20:01,520 --> 00:20:04,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Bucky! Shh!</font>

390
00:20:07,390 --> 00:20:08,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello?</font>

391
00:20:08,770 --> 00:20:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}MOMOTOSE AO</font>

392
00:20:08,780 --> 00:20:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hello, this is Momotose Ao.</i></font>

393
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:15,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm actually contacting all the entrants, 
so I'm sorry I couldn't call you sooner.</i></font>

394
00:20:15,800 --> 00:20:18,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's t-t-totally fine.</font>

395
00:20:18,240 --> 00:20:22,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was s-s-such an honor 
to have you invite me!</font>

396
00:20:22,280 --> 00:20:24,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sorry about today.</i></font>

397
00:20:24,910 --> 00:20:28,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I put you in that group 
because I thought it'd be funny,</i></font>

398
00:20:28,430 --> 00:20:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but they took it a bit too far.</i></font>

399
00:20:30,660 --> 00:20:36,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really didn't mind! I-I'd love to 
collab with you again one day!</font>

400
00:20:36,050 --> 00:20:37,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll reach out again.</i></font>

401
00:20:37,970 --> 00:20:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just like this time,</i></font>

402
00:20:39,980 --> 00:20:41,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I hope you'll bring your advisor with you.</i></font>

403
00:20:43,140 --> 00:20:45,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The reason you've grown so much lately</i></font>

404
00:20:45,350 --> 00:20:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>is because you have 
a capable brain behind you, no?</i></font>

405
00:20:48,290 --> 00:20:51,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd love to speak to your 
advisor directly next time.</i></font>

406
00:20:52,900 --> 00:20:54,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}MOMOTOSE AO</font>

407
00:20:53,580 --> 00:20:54,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>See you then!</i></font>

408
00:20:54,820 --> 00:20:55,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}CALL ENDED</font>

409
00:20:55,780 --> 00:20:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bucky! How'd she know about you?!</font>

410
00:20:58,620 --> 00:20:59,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way.</font>

411
00:20:59,530 --> 00:21:03,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was she able to detect my involvement 
just from the content of the videos?</font>

412
00:21:03,190 --> 00:21:04,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

413
00:21:05,110 --> 00:21:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is what the top 
of the top VTuber is like.</font>

414
00:21:09,250 --> 00:21:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I still have a long way to go.</font>

415
00:21:12,190 --> 00:21:14,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But one day, I'll surely...</font>

416
00:21:16,050 --> 00:21:17,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the matter, Kirino?</font>

417
00:21:18,250 --> 00:21:21,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really caught me 
off guard back there.</font>

418
00:21:21,270 --> 00:21:22,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

419
00:21:26,090 --> 00:21:27,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

420
00:21:28,560 --> 00:21:30,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, that face...</font>

421
00:21:30,950 --> 00:21:32,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So was that a k...</font>

422
00:21:32,600 --> 00:21:34,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it wasn't.</font>

423
00:21:34,690 --> 00:21:38,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my "I wanna use 
the restroom" face.</font>

424
00:21:38,070 --> 00:21:39,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Restroom?</font>

425
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You made my heart race a little.</font>

426
00:21:43,670 --> 00:21:46,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"How dare they hurt my Kirino," you said.</font>

427
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:47,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, wait!</font>

428
00:21:47,580 --> 00:21:49,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forgive me! It was a rush 
of blood to the head!</font>

429
00:21:49,930 --> 00:21:51,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was a slip of the tongue! I'm sorry!</font>

430
00:21:55,310 --> 00:21:57,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do my best.</font>

431
00:21:58,490 --> 00:22:00,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like you said earlier,</font>

432
00:22:02,130 --> 00:22:05,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there won't be so much distance 
between us next time.</font>

433
00:22:06,970 --> 00:22:09,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}WE'LL MAKE DIRECT CONTACT</font>

434
